OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and rather
OL,6,Fbreezy this morning with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading northeastwards. Wind
OL,8,Fand rain easing and skies eventually
OL,9,Fbrightening this afternoon, but
OL,10,Fscattered slow moving showers also
OL,11,Fbuilding. These could be heavy and
OL,12,Fpossibly thundery at times.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers continuing on and off
OL,15,Fthis evening, eventually easing as
OL,16,Fskies clear during the second half of
OL,17,Fthe night. Locally gusty winds
OL,18,Fdeveloping, particularly across and
OL,19,Fclose to higher ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
